# Component Philosophy

Every component should answer:

"Would this belong on a luxury fashion website?"

If not:

Simplify.

Prefer:

- Editorial layouts
- White space
- Typography

Avoid:

- SaaS cards
- Dashboard UI
- Generic templates
- Over-decoration
